   // Client sends: {type: "unsubscribe", goal_id: "abc"}
   // Server tracks subscription map: HashMap<goal_id, HashSet<connection_id>>
   // Only forwards events matching subscribed goal_ids.

   // Phase 1 simpler approach: broadcast all, client filters in JS.
   // Phase 2: server-side filter to reduce bandwidth.
   ```

### Event Flow Diagram

```
Python AgentLoop
    │
    ├── grpc_client.update_goal_progress(goal_id, progress, status, message)
    │       │
    │       ▼
    │   IpcServer::update_goal_progress()
    │       │
    │       ├── goals.update_progress()  → GoalStateStore::update()
    │       │       │
    │       │       └── tx.send(GoalStateNotification { goal_id, progress, status, message })
    │       │               │
    │       │               ▼
    │       │           EventBus.goals (GoalEventBus)
    │       │               │
    │       │               ├── gRPC stream: subscribe_goal_updates() → Python/TS clients
    │       │               │
    │       │               └── Bridge: start_bridge() listens on goals bus
    │       │                       │
    │       │                       ▼
    │       │                   WebSocketServer::push_event(json!({
    │       │                       "type": "goal_update",
    │       │                       "goal_id": "...",
    │       │                       "progress": 0.65,
    │       │                       "status": "active",
    │       │                       "message": "..."
    │       │                   }))
    │       │                       │
    │       │                       ▼
    │       │                   All connected WebSocket clients
    │       │                       │
    │       │                       ▼
    │       │                   Dashboard JS: handleMessage(msg)
    │       │                   → updateProgress(msg)
    │       │
    │       └── metrics.inc_goals()
    │
    ├── grpc_client.submit_eye_reports(...)
    │       │
    │       ▼
    │   IpcServer::submit_eye_reports()
    │       │
    │       ├── events.eye_reports.publish(EyeReportEvent { ... })
    │       │       │
    │       │       └── Bridge: same pattern → WS push
    │       │
    │       └── signal_router.route(&reports) → RoutedSignal
    │
    └── (action logs embedded in update_goal_progress message field)
```

